<A>__{series of establishing shots day exterior scenes of st. louis, particularly the riverside industrial district. even more important to establish than the place is the time: end of summer, 1936. election posters would help, with the republican ones stressing such themes as "burst the roosevelt bubble," "save the american way of life," "vote for landon and knox."}
